                        <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18490917-1809-offence-1 t18490917-geo-1"></join>St. James's, Westminster</placeName>, and stealing 1 snuff-box, value 5<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., and 1 sovereign; the property of <persName id="t18490917-name-604" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18490917-name-604" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
